title: Prescribed Burn - Mt Stranger, Bonython
description:
A prescribed burn is taking place today, Sunday 5 November 2023, at Mt Stranger, Bonython.

Smoke and flames may be visible in these areas while the burn is underway.

This burn is being managed by the ACT Rural Fire Service and is an important tool for managing our land and reducing fire risk.

Call Triple-Zero (000) if you see an unattended fire.
